---
import LegalLayout from '../../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { en as t } from '../../i18n/en';
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Cookie policy — SET"
  description="Cookies used by sustainabletech.ro and how to manage them."
  lang="en"
  lastUpdated="13 May 2026"
  t={t}
>
  <h1>Cookie policy</h1>

  <p>
    The <strong>sustainabletech.ro</strong> website is built minimally and <strong>does not use
    cookies for tracking, marketing, or analytics</strong>. The only cookies that may appear are
    strictly technical, set automatically by our infrastructure provider for security and bot
    protection.
  </p>

  <h2>1. What are cookies</h2>
  <p>
    Cookies are small files stored by your browser when you visit a website, used to retain
    technical preferences or provide security functions.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Cookies we use</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Category</th>
        <th>Cookie</th>
        <th>Purpose</th>
        <th>Duration</th>
        <th>Consent</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Strictly necessary</td>
        <td><code>__cf_bm</code>, <code>cf_clearance</code> (Cloudflare)</td>
        <td>Anti-bot protection, security</td>
        <td>Session — 30 days</td>
        <td>Not required (necessary for operation)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Anonymous analytics</td>
        <td>—</td>
        <td>Cloudflare Web Analytics — does not set cookies, does not track users</td>
        <td>—</td>
        <td>—</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Marketing</td>
        <td>—</td>
        <td>Not used</td>
        <td>—</td>
        <td>—</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>3. How to disable cookies</h2>
  <p>You can disable or delete cookies from your browser settings:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chrome</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/cookies-information-websites-store-on-your-computer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Firefox</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/en-gb/guide/safari/sfri11471/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Safari</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Edge</a></li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Note: disabling strictly necessary cookies may cause technical issues (e.g., Cloudflare may show
    an anti-bot verification page).
  </p>

  <h2>4. Changes</h2>
  <p>
    This policy may be updated. The current version is published here with the date of the latest
    revision (see above).
  </p>

  <h2>5. Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For questions: <a href="mailto:contact@sustainabletech.ro">contact@sustainabletech.ro</a>.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
